			<h1 class="title">Coin Strategy</h1>
			<p class="description">All users have a limited amount of coins to spend in our services. The spent value resets once a day and can be consulted <a href="/userinfo">here</a>.</p>
			<p class="description">In the <a href="/">homepage</a>, it is possible to find the costs of all the services available. Every functionality has a usage cost that is fixed and optionally a cost based on the length of the content.</p>
